# Component architecture

Place components in the correct atomic layer with functional subfolders:

| Layer | Path | Rules |
|-------|------|-------|
| atoms | `atoms/{buttons,brand,nav,actions}/` | Single-purpose; no store access |
| molecules | `molecules/{actions,nav,sparks}/` | Compose atoms only |
| organisms | `organisms/{layout,sparks,prompts}/` | Distinct UI sections; may use stores |
| templates | `templates/layout/` | Page-level layout shells |

Import pattern: `import Button from 'components/atoms/buttons/Button.svelte'`

See [src/components/AGENTS.md](src/components/AGENTS.md) for details.
